CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 1, 2010

[Cite as 12/01/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-5762.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2010-0582. State ex rel. Am. Greetings Corp. v. Fuerst.

In Mandamus and Prohibition. Motion for admission pro hac vice of Kevin K. Green, James I. Jaconette, and Michael F. Ghozland by Jack Landskroner and Paul W. Flowers granted. On S.Ct.Prac.R. 10.5 determination, cause dismissed.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
